</strong></em>\r\n<p align="center"><a href="http://hoclaixeotovip.com/"><strong><img src="http://hoclaixeotovip.com/image/data/icon_10%20-%20Copy.gif" alt="" width="43" height="37" /></strong><strong><strong><img src="http://hoclaixeotovip.com/image/data/icon_10%20-%20Copy.gif" alt="" width="43" height="37" /></strong></strong><strong><strong><strong><img src="http://hoclaixeotovip.com/image/data/icon_10%20-%20Copy.gif" alt="" width="43" height="37" /></strong></strong></strong><img src="http://hoclaixeotovip.com/image/data/icon_11.gif" alt="" width="43" height="38" /><img src="http://hoclaixeotovip.com/image/data/icon_11.gif" alt="" width="43" height="38" /><img src="http://hoclaixeotovip.com/image/data/icon_11.gif" alt="" width="43" height="38" /></a></p>', 'Trang chủ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trang-chu', '', '', '2015-09-26 04:14:31', '2015-09-26 04:14:31', '', 0, 'http://laixe.local/?page_id=515', 0, 'page', '', 0),
